data.description: Just listed! Beautiful brick home on 410 N Ann St. This home sits on a corner lot with a large shade tree out front and a chain link fence surrounding the backyard. This home features 3 bedrooms and 1 1/2 bathrooms with a two car garage attached. The back yard also includes an underground storm shelter that lies steps away from the back door.
